high_descs: Turn right and walk to the knife on the table to your right.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink to the right of the toaster.
Place the knife in the white cup in the sink.
Pick up the white cup from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the toaster to the left of the sink.
Place the cup on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a white cup with a knife in it on the counter in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Move to the corner of the island closest to the stove.
Pick up a knife from the island.
Move to the sink to the left of the fridge.
Put the knife in a cup in the sink.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Move to the left side of the sink to the counter.
Place the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife near the toaster.

high_descs: Go straight ahead and then face right at the end of the white table.
Pick up the knife from the center of the white table.
Carry the knife and turn left to find the sink.
Place the knife inside a mug in the sink.
Pick up the mug and knife from the sink.
Carry the mug a few steps left, to the toaster.
Place the mug on the counter in front of the toast.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife to a mug and place them on the counter.

high_descs: Head around the island to the left, turn right to face the knife on the island.
Pick up the knife on the island.
Turn left, bring the knife to the sink.
Put the knife in the mug in the sink.
Pick up the mug with knife in the sink.
Turn left, bring the mug over to the toaster, turn right to face the toaster on the counter.
Put the mug with knife on the counter, in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with knife on the counter, in front of the toaster.

high_descs: walk to the side of the counter
grab the knife on the counter
turn left, walk across the room  to the sink
put the knife in the cup in the sink
grab the cup from the sink
turn left, walk to the toaster
put the cup in front of the toaster on the counter
anns.task_desc: put the knife in the cup, move the cup to the counter

high_descs: Make your way forward and then turn to your right so you are facing the table
Pick up a knife from the kitchen table
Walk left around the table and then turn left to face the kitchen sink
Put the knife in to the mug that is sitting in the sink
Pick up the mug that has a knife in it
Walk to your left and face back to the toaster
Set down the mug with the knife in it
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a cup and set it down on the kitchen counter
